{"tid":1119413,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【淡友俠落錯車9年駁唔到】愉翠苑無樓睇賣960萬 貴絕新界居屋王","createTime":"2019-04-22T01:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T07:30:42.000Z","uid":43146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3733ab3767c8239f5fdac03bf1c58f42b36c38e5","tid":1119413,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:53:17.000Z","msg":"新界居屋直逼千萬元。萬方地產葉搏麟表示，沙田愉翠苑剛誕下居屋王，位於A座中低層1室，實用面積650方呎，業主於自由市場放售，叫價960萬元，而且單位有租客居住中，不能睇樓，近日零議價下以960萬元易手，呎價14,769元，無論樓價及呎價均創下屋苑新高。愉翠苑今次更打破自己於去年6月造出的913萬元舊紀錄，成為新界史上最貴居屋王。葉搏麟續稱，等同樓價足夠於沙田購入面積相若私人屋苑，如富豪花園、碧濤花園及翠湖花園等，但愉翠苑勝在樓齡較新，且鄰近馬鐵站，交通方便。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190421/59513869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F59513869&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6iC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=e287aa93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190421%2F59513869&h=6f960fb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190421/59513869</a>"},{"pid":"904c28584c3230407c1f0cc9baea442c9a12a746","tid":1119413,"uid":122318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}